rows.label: tlk70000077_03_msg0001
rows.name:
I've been to the Iiran capital a lot for
work, and the level of their industrial
technology never ceases to amaze me!

rows.label: tlk70000077_03_msg0002
rows.name:
I've been a mechanic a long time now,
but the Iirans have got stuff we 
in Superbia just can't understand.

rows.label: tlk70000077_03_msg0003
rows.name:
In particular, there's their theory of
Divine Beast-free high-powered machinery...
Mindblowing, I tell you!

rows.label: tlk70000077_03_msg0004
rows.name:
Back in Superbia, it's usual to use
Divine Beasts as a power source for vehicles.
That's the big difference.

rows.label: tlk70000077_03_msg0005
rows.name:
Iiran cooking, though...
Well...being used to Superbian food
like I am, I couldn't get a taste for it.
